betterquesting:10.desc:8:
- Overworld Surface Changes: Removed Natura Clouds, Natura Redwood Trees and AE2 Meteors (Keeping the Surface Cleaner)
- Overworld Underground Changes: Removed Caves, Mineshafts, Underground Lakes (Help reduce useless underground mob lag, "rare" lakes [use headphones with block volume on high to locate lava early game or ask your neighbours if they can spare some])
- Removed Lootgames & Rogue Dungeons (Pure Spam, Lag, and Beyond Ugly on the World also only single use)
- Angry Mobs: Removed Kamikaze Passive Animals & Angry Pigmen (What a silly mechanic that we never enjoyed)
- No Bloodmoon (Hurts eyes, causes way too much lag, not really a challenge besides server CPU being taxed)
- Nether to Overworld is now 1:1 Scale (gives FAR more nether ore veins per player and promotes the usage of Overworld Travel and maybe even Railroad System! 
- No sleep (makes it fair for all including vampires and hunters). Beds set respawn position (in case of death). Please don't nag people to Sleep.
- World border at 8,000 away from spawn in Overworld, Nether and Twilight Forest

You can find 100% of all changes: [url]https://github.com/StoneLegion/GTNH-2025/commits/main/[/url]
